","msg":"昨晚約11時，一名27歲男子在藍田麗港街27號第7座對開的臨時採樣站完成檢測，並到臨時登記處登記個人資料，期間該名男子懷疑情緒激動及表現不合作，並以硬物襲擊一名24歲女公職人員。該名女公職人員口部受傷，清醒被送往聯合醫院治理。人員經初步調查後，拘捕該名男子涉嫌襲擊致造成實際身體傷害（AOABH）。案件交由觀塘區刑事調查隊第一隊跟進。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24a25998c7c33a597c62cc301357c99c98773eba","tid":2389823,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T07:33:45.000Z","msg":"追打共狗"},{"pid":"a5a5de261c336cffeda0acc8eca896da321d4a76","tid":2389823,"uid":40804,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0d09b3316f75a28e9d0c5ee41f3b558eb605d14","tid":2389823,"uid":207846,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T07:30:38.000Z","msg":"昨晚約11時，一名27歲男子在藍田麗港街27號第7座對開的臨時採樣站完成檢測，並到臨時登記處登記個人資料，期間該名男子懷疑情緒激動及表現不合作，並以硬物襲擊一名24歲女公職人員。該名女公職人員口部受傷，清醒被送往聯合醫院治理。人員經初步調查後，拘捕該名男子涉嫌襲擊致造成實際身體傷害（AOABH）。案件交由觀塘區刑事調查隊第一隊跟進。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T07:35:46.000Z","msg":"抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"721089f538cc52dd6d1d6f040e56e2ce82a4c00b","tid":2389823,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29bc8e6d58f17bbd83b713bd5a7ebac174aeebee","tid":2389823,"uid":52946,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T07:20:06.000Z","msg":"講2句又暴力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 